  "description": "<p>分类: <a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/category/peripherals/\" rel=\"tag\">外围设备</a></p><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"cn.engadget.com/2014/01/06/enerplex-jumpr-slate-external-battery/\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://o.aolcdn.com/hss/storage/adam/fe4cc0fcbb2bd203373ba5566b2f594a/enerplex-jumpr-slate-hands-on.jpg\" /></a></div>\n\n<div><br />\n又大又厚的大容量外置电池虽然可以给装置很高的续航力，不过携带外出比较不便。而 EnerPlex 在 CES 2014 所展示这款 Jumpr Slate 大容量外置电池则比较「合理」一点。它有着 6.7mm 的纤薄厚度，内置 2.4 amps 的 5,500mAh 或 10,000mAh 电量，可经两个全尺寸 USB 或一个 micro-USB 跟其他装置连接，机身还有四个 LED 灯用作显示电量。它将于一月完结前在美国上市，要价 US$59（约 365 元人民币）或 US99（约 605 元人民币），视乎容量而定。<br />\n<div class=\"postgallery\"><p><strong>Gallery: <a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/photos/enerplex-jumpr-slate-hands-on-at-ces-2014/\">EnerPlex Jumpr Slate hands-on at CES 2014</a></strong></p><a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/photos/enerplex-jumpr-slate-hands-on-at-ces-2014/6420510/\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://www.blogcdn.com/cn.engadget.com/media/2014/01/enerplex-jumpr-slate-2014-01-06-1_thumbnail.jpg\" title=\"\" /></a><a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/photos/enerplex-jumpr-slate-hands-on-at-ces-2014/6420511/\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://www.blogcdn.com/cn.engadget.com/media/2014/01/enerplex-jumpr-slate-2014-01-06-1-1_thumbnail.jpg\" title=\"\" /></a><a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/photos/enerplex-jumpr-slate-hands-on-at-ces-2014/6420512/\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://www.blogcdn.com/cn.engadget.com/media/2014/01/enerplex-jumpr-slate-2014-01-06-2-1_thumbnail.jpg\" title=\"\" /></a><a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/photos/enerplex-jumpr-slate-hands-on-at-ces-2014/6420513/\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://www.blogcdn.com/cn.engadget.com/media/2014/01/enerplex-jumpr-slate-2014-01-06-3-1_thumbnail.jpg\" title=\"\" /></a></div><br />\n<br />\n引用来源：<a href=\"http://www.engadget.com/2014/01/05/enerplex-jumpr-slate-external-battery/\">Engadget</a></div><p><h6 style=\"clear: both; padding: 8px 0 0 0; height: 2px; font-size: 1px; border: 0; margin: 0;